107
00:23:46,720 --> 00:23:53,599
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, onda je 1925.

108
00:23:53,920 --> 00:23:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] godine imenovan magistrom Bogoslova.

109
00:23:56,480 --> 00:23:57,519
[SPEAKER_00] I zašto je to važno?

110
00:23:57,839 --> 00:24:00,960
