141
00:28:23,680 --> 00:28:24,480
[SPEAKER_00] I morali smo ići.

142
00:28:24,799 --> 00:28:26,240
[SPEAKER_01] I koliko ste morali biti u JNA?

143
00:28:26,799 --> 00:28:28,640
